product_name: Leatherman Crater c33 Fine Edge Knife
long_description: Made for outdoor tasks, the Leatherman Crater c33 knife combines a fine-edge blade with a handy carabiner clip and bottle opener. Blade is made of 420HC stainless steel; it features a thumb stud and Blade Launcher(R) assist for easy opening. This knife is built tough with a glass-filled nylon handle and locking liner. The Leatherman Crater c33 knife features a carabiner clip, bottle opener and removable pocket clip.
